videos.headline: Old Dominion lineman recovers fumble in end zone for a big-man TD
videos.description: OT Nick Saldiveri recovers the fumble in the end zone for a Monarchs touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blake Watson scores 9-yard Rushing TD vs. Charlotte) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Elijah Davis maneuvers through Charlotte's defense for an Old Dominion TD
videos.description: Elijah Davis makes a few cuts and walks in to the end zone untouched, extending the Monarchs' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (End Zone! Elijah Davis scores 12-yard Rushing touchdown vs. Charlotte) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ali Jennings makes a few moves and finds pay dirt
videos.description: Ali Jennings hauls in the catch and makes a few moves on his way to a Monarchs touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ali Jennings makes the grab for 46-yard Receiving touchdown) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chris Reynolds throws a dime to put the 49ers on the board
videos.description: Elijah Spencer hauls in a beauty from Chris Reynolds to put Charlotte on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chris Reynolds with 19-yard touchdown Pass to Elijah Spencer vs. Old Dominion) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ali Jennings makes an amazing TD catch with his fingertips
videos.description: Ali Jennings goes full extension with his arms to haul in a nice touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ali Jennings makes catch for 34-yard Receiving TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Old Dominion QB's pass hits back of lineman's head, gets returned for pick-6
videos.description: Hayden Wolff's pass hits his lineman in the back of the head and goes into the air before it's picked off by Luke Martin, who takes it back for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Old Dominion QB's pass hits back of lineman's head, gets returned for pick-6) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Grant Dubose snags the ball over the defenders head for a 49ers TD

videos.headline: Calvin Camp powers his way into the end zone for a 49ers TD
videos.description: Calvin Camp takes it up the gut and finds pay dirt to tie the game at 28-28.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Calvin Camp crosses goal-line for 6-yard Rushing TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blake Watson muscles his way past the goal line for a Monarchs TD
videos.description: Blake Watson keeps pushing and driving his feet until he finds pay dirt to give Old Dominion the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blake Watson runs for 3-yard Rushing touchdown) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blake Watson finds the end zone for his 2nd rushing TD
videos.description: Blake Watson drives his way past the goal line for his second rushing touchdown, extending the Monarchs' lead.
